      <t>&lt;p&gt;This document enhances the BGP Cease NOTIFICATION message "Administrative Shutdown" and "Administrative Reset" subcodes for operators to transmit a short freeform message to describe why a BGP session was shutdown or reset.  This document updates RFC 4486.&lt;/p&gt;</t>
